<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10109761>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–28. Daveyoungana longibrachia sp. nov., male holotype. 15, head and thorax, dorsal view. 16, head and thorax, ventral view. 17, head and thorax, lateral view. 18, forewing. 19–28, male terminalia: 19, sternite VIII, ventral view. 20, pygofer, dorsal view, 21, pygofer and subgenital plate, lateral view. 22, ventral process of pygofer, lateral view. 23, ventral process of pygofer, ventral view. 24, subgenital plate, ventral view. 25, connective, dorsal view. 26, style, dorsal view. 27, aedeagus, lateral view. 28, aedeagus, posterior view. Scale bars: 15–18 = 1.0 mm, 19–21 = 0.5 mm, 22–28 = 0.25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10109761/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10109763>
    dc:description "FIGURES 29–35. Daveyoungana longibrachia sp. nov., female paratype. 29, sternite VII, ventral view. 30, pygofer, lateral view. 31, first valvifer and first valvula, lateral view. 32, apex of first valvula, lateral view. 33, second valvula, lateral view. 34, apex of second valvula, lateral view. 35, gonoplac, lateral view. Scale bars = 0.5mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10109763/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10109769>
    dc:description "FIGURES 57–62. Holotypes habitus, dorsal view (left) and lateral view (right). 57, 58, Daveyoungana blockeri sp. nov., 59, 60, Daveyoungana longibrachia sp. nov., 61, 62, Daveyoungana pentacorni sp. nov. Scale bars = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10109769/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

